      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is deployed under a documented software quality plan. Version control via Git with tagged release builds, automated regression tests covering 94% of core solver paths, and a formal issue-tracking system are all verified. SQA level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
