      "rationale": "Not formally assessed at MRL 2 for this COU. Morrison et al. report standard PBS-glycerol blood analog preparation procedures. Sample characterization is considered adequate for the level of fidelity required. Scoped out per MRL 2 factor applicability matrix."
    },
