    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against the MRL 2 factor applicability matrix. Seven factors were formally assessed with structured evidence; all seven meet or exceed their required levels. Six factors were scoped out as not required at MRL 2 given the device class and model influence classification. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the use of the CFD model for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The decision to Accept is consistent with the structured factor evidence reviewed by the assessment team.",
